heading: Plucked instrument trios.
general-note: Here are entered collections of trios not in a specific form or of a specific type for various combinations of three plucked stringed instruments. Individual plucked instrument trios and collections not in a specific form or of a specific type for a single combination of instruments are entered under this heading followed by the instruments in alphabetical order..
Collections of compositions for three plucked keyboard instruments are entered under. Keyboard instrument ensembles, Harpsichord ensembles, and similar headings..
